<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Culturally Ai — Done-For-You Resumes for Experienced Job Seekers</title>
<meta name="description" content="Culturally Ai writes polished, ATS-aligned resumes and LinkedIn profiles for professionals with 5+ years of experience who are ready to move into stronger opportunities.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,72,400;0,72,500;0,72,600;1,72,500&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>

  /* ============ TOKENS ============ */
  :root{
    --ink:#0E1D33;          /* primary navy — headlines, dark surfaces */
    --ink-deep:#081120;     /* deepest navy — footer depth */
    --bone:#F7F6F2;         /* page background, warm neutral (not cream) */
    --paper:#FFFFFF;        /* card surfaces */
    --charcoal:#232A38;     /* body copy */
    --slate:#6B7385;        /* muted text, "struck-through" old phrasing */
    --brass:#C99A3C;        /* decorative accent — buttons, seals, rules */
    --brass-deep:#8A6526;   /* text-safe accent — links, redline insertions */
    --border:#E3DFD3;       /* hairline border on bone */
    --border-dark:rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
    --shadow:0 24px 48px -16px rgba(14,29,51,0.22);
    --radius:14px;
    --display:'Newsreader', Georgia, serif;
    --body:'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    --mono:'IBM Plex Mono', 'SF Mono', monospace;
  }

  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth; scroll-padding-top:88px;}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    html{scroll-behavior:auto;}
    *{animation-duration:0.001ms !important; animation-iteration-count:1 !important; transition-duration:0.001ms !important;}
  }

  body{
    margin:0;
    font-family:var(--body);
    color:var(--charcoal);
    background:var(--bone);
    line-height:1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }

  h1,h2,h3{
    font-family:var(--display);
    color:var(--ink);
    margin:0 0 0.5em;
    font-weight:500;
    letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  }

  p{margin:0 0 1em; color:var(--charcoal);}
  a{color:var(--brass-deep); text-decoration:none;}
  img,svg{display:block; max-width:100%;}

  .skip-link{
    position:absolute; left:-999px; top:0;
    background:var(--brass); color:var(--ink); padding:10px 16px;
    font-weight:600; z-index:200; border-radius:0 0 8px 0;
  }
  .skip-link:focus{left:0;}

  :focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--brass-deep); outline-offset:3px; border-radius:4px;}

  .wrap{max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 28px;}
  .eyebrow{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12.5px; letter-spacing:0.09em;
    text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--brass-deep); font-weight:600;
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{content:''; width:18px; height:1px; background:var(--brass-deep); display:inline-block;}

  section{padding:96px 0;}
  #services, #process, #faq{scroll-margin-top:88px;}
  @media (max-width:760px){ section{padding:64px 0;} }

  .reveal{opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px); transition:opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;}
  .reveal.is-visible{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}

  /* ============ NAV ============ */
  header.site-nav{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:100;
    background:var(--ink); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-dark);
  }
  .nav-row{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:18px 28px; max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto;
  }
  .brand{
    font-family:var(--display); font-style:italic; font-weight:500;
    color:#FBF8F2; font-size:21px; letter-spacing:0.01em;
  }
  .brand span{color:var(--brass);}
  nav.primary-links{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:34px;}
  nav.primary-links a.nav-link{
    color:#D8DCE6; font-size:14.5px; font-weight:500;
  }
  nav.primary-links a.nav-link:hover{color:#fff;}
  .btn{
    font-family:var(--body); font-weight:600; font-size:14.5px;
    padding:11px 20px; border-radius:8px; border:1px solid transparent;
    cursor:pointer; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    transition:transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease;
  }
  .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);}
  .btn-brass{background:var(--brass); color:var(--ink);}
  .btn-brass:hover{background:#D8AC52; box-shadow:0 8px 18px -8px rgba(201,154,60,0.6);}
  .btn-outline-dark{background:transparent; color:#fff; border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);}
  .btn-outline-dark:hover{border-color:#fff;}
  .btn-outline{background:transparent; color:var(--ink); border-color:var(--ink);}
  .btn-outline:hover{background:var(--ink); color:#fff;}
  .btn-ghost{background:transparent; color:var(--brass-deep); padding:11px 6px;}

  .hamburger{display:none; background:none; border:0; color:#fff; cursor:pointer; padding:8px;}
  .hamburger svg{width:24px; height:24px;}
  .mobile-panel{display:none; flex-direction:column; gap:2px; padding:0 28px 20px; background:var(--ink);}
  .mobile-panel a{color:#D8DCE6; padding:12px 4px; font-size:15px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-dark);}
  .mobile-panel.open{display:flex;}

  @media (max-width:860px){
    nav.primary-links{display:none;}
    .hamburger{display:inline-flex;}
  }

  /* ============ HERO ============ */
  .hero{
    background:var(--ink);
    padding:80px 0 96px;
  }
  .hero-grid{
    display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.05fr 0.95fr; gap:54px; align-items:start;
  }
  @media (max-width:920px){ .hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:40px;} }

  .hero-copy h1{
    color:#FBF8F2; font-size:clamp(34px,4.4vw,54px); line-height:1.1; margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .hero-copy .sub{color:#C9D0DD; font-size:18px; max-width:480px; margin-bottom:18px;}
  .hero-copy .credibility-line{
    color:var(--brass); font-family:var(--mono); font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.02em;
    margin-bottom:26px; line-height:1.6;
  }
  .hero-ctas{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:14px; margin-bottom:28px;}
  .proof-row{display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;}
  .proof-chip{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.03em; color:#E7E2D4;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
    padding:7px 12px; border-radius:999px;
  }

  /* Signature element: the redline resume card */
  .redline-card{
    background:var(--paper); border-radius:var(--radius); box-shadow:0 30px 60px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    padding:30px 30px 26px; transform:rotate(1.2deg);
    border:1px solid var(--border); position:relative;
  }
  .redline-card::before{
    content:''; position:absolute; top:-14px; right:26px; width:64px; height:64px;
    background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #E6C272, var(--brass-deep));
    border-radius:50%; box-shadow:0 10px 18px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
  }
  .redline-card::after{
    content:'✓'; position:absolute; top:6px; right:50px; color:var(--ink);
    font-size:22px; font-weight:700; font-family:var(--body);
  }
  .redline-card .doc-label{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--slate); margin-bottom:16px; display:block;
  }
  .redline-card .field-label{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px; color:var(--brass-deep); text-transform:uppercase;
    letter-spacing:0.06em; margin-bottom:8px; display:block;
  }
  .redline-old{
    font-family:var(--body); font-size:15.5px; color:var(--slate);
    text-decoration:line-through; text-decoration-color:#C4392E; text-decoration-thickness:1.5px;
    margin-bottom:18px; line-height:1.5;
  }
  .redline-new{
    font-family:var(--display); font-size:18px; color:var(--ink);
    border-bottom:2px solid var(--brass); display:inline; padding-bottom:2px; line-height:1.5;
  }
  .redline-new .typed::after{
    content:'|'; color:var(--brass-deep); animation:blink 1s steps(1) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes blink{50%{opacity:0;}}
  .redline-foot{
    margin-top:22px; padding-top:18px; border-top:1px dashed var(--border);
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
  }
  .redline-foot span{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px; color:var(--slate);}
  .stamp{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:10.5px; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--brass-deep);
    border:1.5px solid var(--brass-deep); padding:4px 9px; border-radius:5px; transform:rotate(-3deg);
    display:inline-block;
  }

  /* ============ PROBLEM / SOLUTION ============ */
  .problem-head{max-width:680px; margin-bottom:48px;}
  .problem-head h2{font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,36px);}
  .three-cards{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:24px;}
  @media (max-width:860px){ .three-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr;} }
  .pcard{
    background:var(--paper); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:var(--radius);
    padding:28px 26px; position:relative;
  }
  .pcard .mark{
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; color:var(--brass-deep); letter-spacing:0.05em;
    margin-bottom:14px; display:block;
  }
  .pcard h3{font-size:19px; margin-bottom:8px;}
  .pcard p{font-size:15px; color:var(--slate); margin:0;}

  /* ============ CREDIBILITY BAND ============ */
  .credibility{
    background:var(--ink); color:#E9E6DC; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .credibility::before{
    content:''; position:absolute; inset:0;
    background:radial-gradient(800px 400px at 85% 0%, rgba(201,154,60,0.10), transparent 60%);
  }
  .credibility .wrap{position:relative;}
  .cred-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr; gap:56px; align-items:start;}
  @media (max-width:920px){ .cred-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:40px;} }
  .credibility h2{color:#FBF8F2; font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,34px);}
  .credibility p.lead{color:#C9D0DD; font-size:16.5px; max-width:520px;}
  .trust-list{list-style:none; margin:26px 0 0; padding:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px;}
  .trust-list li{
    display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:flex-start; color:#D8DCE6; font-size:15px;
  }
  .trust-list li::before{
    content:''; flex-shrink:0; width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--brass); margin-top:8px;
  }
  .stat-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:18px;}
  .stat-box{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border:1px solid var(--border-dark); border-radius:12px;
    padding:22px 18px;
  }
  .stat-box .num{font-family:var(--display); font-size:30px; color:var(--brass); font-weight:600;}
  .stat-box .label{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11.5px; color:#B7BECC; letter-spacing:0.03em; margin-top:4px;}
  .bio-note{
    margin-top:26px; padding-top:22px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-dark);
    display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:flex-start;
  }
  .monogram{
    width:46px; height:46px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--brass); color:var(--ink);
    font-family:var(--display); font-weight:600; font-size:16px; display:flex; align-items:center;
    justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0;
  }
  .bio-note p{font-size:14px; color:#C9D0DD; margin:0;}
  .bio-note p strong{color:#fff;}

  /* ============ PRICING ============ */
  .pricing-head{text-align:center; max-width:620px; margin:0 auto 50px;}
  .pricing-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:24px; align-items:stretch;}
  @media (max-width:920px){ .pricing-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr; max-width:480px; margin:0 auto;} }
  .price-card{
    background:var(--paper); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:var(--radius);
    padding:32px 28px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; position:relative;
  }
  .price-card.featured{
    border-color:var(--brass); box-shadow:0 28px 50px -22px rgba(201,154,60,0.4); transform:translateY(-8px);
  }
  .featured-tag{
    position:absolute; top:-13px; left:28px; background:var(--ink); color:var(--brass);
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase;
    padding:5px 11px; border-radius:5px;
  }
  .price-card .tier-name{font-size:13px; font-family:var(--mono); color:var(--brass-deep); letter-spacing:0.04em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:10px;}
  .price-card .amount{font-family:var(--display); font-size:36px; color:var(--ink); margin-bottom:6px;}
  .price-card .tier-desc{font-size:14px; color:var(--slate); margin-bottom:20px;}
  .price-card ul{list-style:none; margin:0 0 26px; padding:0; flex-grow:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:11px;}
  .price-card ul li{font-size:14.5px; color:var(--charcoal); padding-left:22px; position:relative;}
  .price-card ul li::before{content:'—'; position:absolute; left:0; color:var(--brass-deep);}
  .price-card .btn{width:100%; justify-content:center;}

  /* ============ WHO IT'S FOR ============ */
  .who-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:0.9fr 1.1fr; gap:54px; align-items:center;}
  @media (max-width:860px){ .who-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:30px;} }
  .who-list{list-style:none; margin:0; padding:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px;}
  .who-list li{
    display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:flex-start; font-size:16px; color:var(--charcoal);
    background:var(--paper); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:10px; padding:16px 18px;
  }
  .who-list li::before{
    content:'✓'; flex-shrink:0; width:22px; height:22px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--brass);
    color:var(--ink); font-size:12px; font-weight:700; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    margin-top:1px;
  }

  /* ============ WHAT YOU RECEIVE / TURNAROUND ============ */
  .receive-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:64px;}
  @media (max-width:860px){ .receive-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:44px;} }
  .receive-col h2{font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,34px); margin-bottom:12px;}
  .receive-col .lead{color:var(--slate); font-size:15.5px; max-width:480px; margin-bottom:26px;}
  .ring-list{list-style:none; margin:0; padding:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:17px;}
  .ring-list li{display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:14px; font-weight:600; font-size:15.5px; color:var(--ink);}
  .ring-list li::before{content:''; flex-shrink:0; width:17px; height:17px; border-radius:50%; border:2.5px solid var(--brass); margin-top:3px;}

  /* ============ PROCESS ============ */
  .process-head{max-width:620px; margin:0 auto 50px; text-align:center;}
  .process-head .eyebrow{justify-content:center;}
  .process-head p.lead{color:var(--slate); font-size:15.5px; margin-top:14px;}
  .process-cards{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr); gap:18px;}
  @media (max-width:1060px){ .process-cards{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);} }
  @media (max-width:620px){ .process-cards{grid-template-columns:1fr;} }
  .process-card{
    background:var(--paper); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:26px 22px;
  }
  .process-card .pno{
    width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:9px; background:var(--brass); color:var(--ink);
    font-family:var(--mono); font-weight:700; font-size:14px;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .process-card h3{font-size:17px; margin-bottom:8px; font-family:var(--body); font-weight:700;}
  .process-card p{font-size:14px; color:var(--slate); margin:0;}

  /* ============ FINAL CTA ============ */
  .final-cta{
    background:var(--ink); color:#fff; border-radius:20px; padding:64px 48px;
    text-align:center; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .final-cta::before{
    content:''; position:absolute; inset:0;
    background:radial-gradient(600px 300px at 50% 0%, rgba(201,154,60,0.16), transparent 65%);
  }
  .final-cta h2{color:#FBF8F2; font-size:clamp(26px,3.4vw,36px); position:relative;}
  .final-cta p{color:#C9D0DD; max-width:560px; margin:0 auto 28px; position:relative; font-size:16px;}
  .final-cta .micro{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; color:#9AA3B5; margin-top:18px; position:relative;}

  /* ============ FAQ ============ */
  .faq-head{max-width:560px; margin-bottom:40px;}
  .faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .faq-q{
    width:100%; text-align:left; background:none; border:0; padding:20px 0;
    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:16px;
    cursor:pointer; font-family:var(--body); font-weight:600; font-size:16.5px; color:var(--ink);
  }
  .faq-q .plus{font-family:var(--mono); font-size:18px; color:var(--brass-deep); transition:transform 0.2s ease; flex-shrink:0;}
  .faq-item.open .plus{transform:rotate(45deg);}
  .faq-a{max-height:0; overflow:hidden; transition:max-height 0.3s ease;}
  .faq-a p{padding:0 0 20px; color:var(--slate); font-size:15px; max-width:680px;}

  /* ============ FOOTER ============ */
  footer{background:var(--ink-deep); color:#9AA3B5; padding:48px 0 32px;}
  .footer-row{display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:flex-start; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:24px;}
  .footer-brand{font-family:var(--display); font-style:italic; color:#E9E6DC; font-size:19px;}
  .footer-links{display:flex; gap:24px; flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .footer-links a{color:#9AA3B5; font-size:13.5px;}
  .footer-links a:hover{color:#fff;}
  .footer-fine{margin-top:30px; padding-top:24px; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); font-size:12.5px; color:#6E7587; max-width:680px;}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<a href="#main" class="skip-link">Skip to content</a>

<header class="site-nav">
  <div class="nav-row">
    <a href="#" class="brand">Culturally <span>Ai</span></a>
    <nav class="primary-links" aria-label="Primary">
      <a class="nav-link" href="#services">Services</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#process">Process</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      <a class="btn btn-brass js-intake" href="#">Start Private Resume Intake</a>
    </nav>
    <button class="hamburger" id="hamburgerBtn" aria-label="Open menu" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobilePanel">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/></svg>
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="mobile-panel" id="mobilePanel">
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#process">Process</a>
    <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
    <a class="js-intake" href="#">Start Private Resume Intake →</a>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="main">

  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--brass);">Done-for-you, not DIY</span>
        <h1>Done-For-You Resumes for Experienced Job Seekers</h1>
        <p class="sub">Culturally Ai writes polished, ATS-aligned resumes and LinkedIn profiles for professionals with 5+ years of experience who are ready to move into stronger opportunities.</p>
        <p class="credibility-line">Written by a recruiter with cross-industry experience · 10+ years supporting career transitions · 35+ happy customers</p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a class="btn btn-brass js-intake" href="#">Start Private Resume Intake</a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="#services">View Packages</a>
        </div>
        <div class="proof-row">
          <span class="proof-chip">RECRUITER-WRITTEN</span>
          <span class="proof-chip">10+ YEARS EXPERIENCE</span>
          <span class="proof-chip">35+ HAPPY CUSTOMERS</span>
          <span class="proof-chip">ATS-ALIGNED</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="redline-card" id="redlineCard">
          <span class="doc-label">Resume Draft — Experience</span>
          <span class="field-label">Before</span>
          <p class="redline-old">Responsible for managing daily operations and overseeing staff scheduling.</p>
          <span class="field-label">After</span>
          <p class="redline-new" id="redlineNew"><span class="typed" id="typedText"></span></p>
          <div class="redline-foot">
            <span>EDITED · ATS KEYWORDS MATCHED</span>
            <span class="stamp">REVIEWED</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ PROBLEM / SOLUTION ============ -->
  <section class="reveal">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="problem-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">The problem</span>
        <h2>You Bring the Experience. We Build the Resume.</h2>
        <p>You should not have to guess which keywords matter, how to explain your career story, or how to turn years of work into strong resume bullets. This is a done-for-you service led by someone who understands how recruiters read resumes across industries.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="three-cards">
        <div class="pcard">
          <span class="mark">01 — PERSPECTIVE</span>
